item.description:
Hi everyone,

The meet up server seems to be doing some wacky stuff. If you didn't receive it the first time here are the details for today:

Its suppose to be close to 70 today. A perfect day for hiking. Lets meet at Lynn Woods and hike for about
1-1.5 an hour at a moderate pace. Hiking boots and water are recommended.

We'll me at 2:30 in the parking lot (please not there are 2 parking lots - (you want the Pennybrook Rd lot) and start hiking no later than 2:45. If you are lost my cell is 508-472-7900.
